---
title: Korean BBQ Tofu Tacos with Quick–Pickled Onion & Soy Mayo
description: Little on time and big on flavour, these simple tacos have sweet and salty glazed tofu, crunchy pickled onion and soy mayo all wrapped up in a warm tortilla. Now that's a lot of good things to smile about!
